ww.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/M%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-2-C%E1%BB%ADu-v%E1%BA%A1n-%C4%91o%C3%A0n-phong-k%C3%BD-t%C3%ADch-t%E1%BA%B1ng/poem-wkCXUydbKG3TixWOKpwyFg">Mạn hứng kỳ 2 (Cửu vạn đoàn phong ký tích tằng) - 漫興其二（九萬摶風記昔曾）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%C3%B3ng-ng%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-j1NsF-L-kuqg8ZJRLu1Sfw">Phóng ngôn kỳ 3 - 放言其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/T%C3%A2n-lang/poem-i3_OT8pP-hlCO0Tgnr_YMw">Tân lang - 檳榔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/T%C3%A2n-qu%C3%A1n-ng%E1%BB%A5-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-15/poem-ZzibyZU3uWiwUYBRDFmI8w">Tân quán ngụ hứng kỳ 15 - 津觀寓興其十五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
